title: Oumaima Aziz
data: Oumaima Aziz (born 1 March 2001) is an inactive Moroccan tennis player. Aziz has a career-high ITF juniors ranking of 185, achieved on 26 March 2018. She made her WTA Tour main-draw debut at the 2018 Rabat Grand Prix in the doubles tournament, partnering Diae El Jardi.
